  { q: 'Do you provide compliance certificates?', a: 'While Tennessee itself may not always mandate formal "hood cleaning certificates," we clean all systems to the <strong>full NFPA 96 standards</strong> and provide <strong>comprehensive digital photo evidence and detailed reports</strong> that consistently satisfy local fire marshals, health inspectors, and insurance requirements.' },
  { q: 'How quickly can I get service, especially for an emergency?', a: 'For <strong>emergencies</strong>, we offer <strong>24/7 same-day response</strong> to get your kitchen back online as quickly as possible. For scheduled work, we typically book appointments within 1\u20133 business days, often accommodating urgent requests.' },
